{
  "texts": [
    "This dual-mode object detection ensures adaptability and versatility, capable of handling both pre-captured images and live video streams.",
    "Whether the need is for detailed analysis of static content or real-time responsiveness in dynamic environments, our system's dual-mode capabilities provide a flexible and encompassing solution for diverse use cases.",
    "III.SINGLE SHOT DETECTOR Lately, the domain of computer vision has witnessed a transformative shift propelled by advancements in deep learning methodologies.",
    "Among the myriad of innovations, the Single Shot Multibox Detector (SSD) stands out as a pioneering approach to object detection, offering unparalleled speed and accuracy.",
    "Developed to address the limitations of conventional object detection techniques, SSD amalgamates the efficiency of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) with the elegance of region proposal networks, establishing itself as a cornerstone in real-time object detection."
  ]
}